          "achie_count_1": "1549",
          "achie_1": "Happy clients",
          "achie_icon_2": "<svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" data-prefix=\"fas\" data-icon=\"trophy\" role=\"img\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" viewbox=\"0 0 576 512\" class=\"svg-inline--fa fa-trophy fa-w-18 fa-2x\"><path fill=\"currentColor\" d=\"M552 64H448V24c0-13.3-10.7-24-24-24H152c-13.3 0-24 10.7-24 24v40H24C10.7 64 0 74.7 0 88v56c0 35.7 22.5 72.4 61.9 100.7 31.5 22.7 69.8 37.1 110 41.7C203.3 338.5 240 360 240 360v72h-48c-35.3 0-64 20.7-64 56v12c0 6.6 5.4 12 12 12h296c6.6 0 12-5.4 12-12v-12c0-35.3-28.7-56-64-56h-48v-72s36.7-21.5 68.1-73.6c40.3-4.6 78.6-19 110-41.7 39.3-28.3 61.9-65 61.9-100.7V88c0-13.3-10.7-24-24-24zM99.3 192.8C74.9 175.2 64 155.6 64 144v-16h64.2c1 32.6 5.8 61.2 12.8 86.2-15.1-5.2-29.2-12.4-41.7-21.4zM512 144c0 16.1-17.7 36.1-35.3 48.8-12.5 9-26.7 16.2-41.8 21.4 7-25 11.8-53.6 12.8-86.2H512v16z\" class=\"\"></path></svg>",
          "achie_count_2": "37",
          "achie_2": "Award winning",
          "achie_icon_3": "<svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" data-prefix=\"fas\" data-icon=\"users\" role=\"img\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" viewbox=\"0 0 640 512\" class=\"svg-inline--fa fa-users fa-w-20 fa-2x\"><path fill=\"currentColor\" d=\"M96 224c35.3 0 64-28.7 64-64s-28.7-64-64-64-64 28.7-64 64 28.7 64 64 64zm448 0c35.3 0 64-28.7 64-64s-28.7-64-64-64-64 28.7-64 64 28.7 64 64 64zm32 32h-64c-17.6 0-33.5 7.1-45.1 18.6 40.3 22.1 68.9 62 75.1 109.4h66c17.7 0 32-14.3 32-32v-32c0-35.3-28.7-64-64-64zm-256 0c61.9 0 112-50.1 112-112S381.9 32 320 32 208 82.1 208 144s50.1 112 112 112zm76.8 32h-8.3c-20.8 10-43.9 16-68.5 16s-47.6-6-68.5-16h-8.3C179.6 288 128 339.6 128 403.2V432c0 26.5 21.5 48 48 48h288c26.5 0 48-21.5 48-48v-28.8c0-63.6-51.6-115.2-115.2-115.2zm-223.7-13.4C161.5 263.1 145.6 256 128 256H64c-35.3 0-64 28.7-64 64v32c0 17.7 14.3 32 32 32h65.9c6.3-47.4 34.9-87.3 75.2-109.4z\" class=\"\"></path></svg>",
          "achie_count_3": "7",
          "achie_3": "Team members",
          "chooseus_enable": true,
          "chooseus_title1": "Our design",
          "chooseus_des": "<p><a href=\"https://ap2020.myshopify.com\">2020</a> has always been a design company at heart. The Innovation Department, responsible for the development of new concepts and products and counting more than 70 employees to date, is the beating heart and the engine of the company.<br> The original Shopify theme, the <a href=\"https://ap2020.myshopify.com\">2020</a>, breathes the legacy of 15 years of the design. Having evolved over time, the iconic all-in-one Shopify theme remains unsurpassed with regards to its defining functionalities.</p>\n<p>Now all of our Shopify theme, including the <a href=\"https://ap2020.myshopify.com\">2020</a>, share the same design principles: design and engineering, aesthetics and functionality, form and function, have come together seamlessly.</p>",
          "chooseus_title2": "Why choose us",
          "chooseus_question1": "Quality is our key business",
          "chooseus_answer1": "Quality has always been at the core of us, as we want our products to last whilst being used every day. To ensure the highest quality, we like to be in charge of the entire development and production process – from the first sketch to the final Shopify theme.",
          "chooseus_question2": "Full support",
          "chooseus_answer2": "Quality has always been at the core of us, as we want our products to last whilst being used every day. To ensure the highest quality, we like to be in charge of the entire development and production process – from the first sketch to the final Shopify theme.",
          "chooseus_question3": "Free returns",
          "chooseus_answer3": "Quality has always been at the core of us, as we want our products to last whilst being used every day. To ensure the highest quality, we like to be in charge of the entire development and production process – from the first sketch to the final Shopify theme.",
          "chooseus_question4": "Product Design",
          "chooseus_answer4": "Quality has always been at the core of us, as we want our products to last whilst being used every day. To ensure the highest quality, we like to be in charge of the entire development and production process – from the first sketch to the final Shopify theme.",
          "team_enable": true,
