              "info": "",
              "rate": 5,
              "quote": "I’ve been taking this product for 3 months now and I have noticed that it keeps my weight from going up. I’m in menopause and I don’t workout. I’ve beengaining weight so I tried the product. I take one capsule 30 minutes before each meal. I’m not a doctor or nurse just a regular customer."
