          "quote_YAaarr": {
            "type": "quote",
            "settings": {
              "title": "Energy and a smaller appetite!",
              "avatar": "shopify://shop_images/user.png",
              "author": "Jenn & Jason",
              "info": "",
              "rate": 5,
              "quote": "So I’ve been taking this for maybe 5 days now. Everyday so far I have energy! I’ve battled with major fatigue for quite a few years. Took various herbs to combat that and have since felt decent enough with a decent amount of energy but not what I used to have. Well now that I’ve been taking Berberine I have been tackling chores I have put off for months! Not a jittery energy just not feeling pulled down by lack of energy. Also, it’s been curbing my appetite! I’ve gained weight in the recent years and it’s not like I pig out but I don’t normally eat petite portions. And if it’s on my plate I’ll eat it. I felt like my trigger to tell me I’m full was malfunctioning. Well, it’s like instantly I’m not feeling like I need to snack. I have been wanting to cut carbs and have cut down on them but now it’s pretty easy to just say no. And I feel like I get full faster. Im eating less at meals just because I’m full! What a concept! I could see that alone helping me with weight loss. After learning more about insulin resistance I believe I have that as I have the symptoms. Will see if my other symptoms go down with this but so far so good!"
            }
          },
